content: bguiz: Merged a significant PR (#3589) that allows the Eliza client to configure the Eliza server base URL, involving substantial code changes (+15,697/-370,144 lines). Created two feature-related issues (#3585 and #3567) focused on configuration improvements, both of which were subsequently closed. Contributed small but focused code modifications across three different file types (code, docs, and config) with a total of +18/-1 lines.
